---
title: BBQ Baby Back Ribs & Cheesy Buffalo Mac with Buttermilk Ranch Slaw
description: Ready to serve up a full-on feast of a cookout for your lucky friends and family? (Or just for yourself, with a banquet’s-worth of leftovers? Hey, that sounds pretty great to us, too.) Here, we send you all the fixin’s so you can spend less time planning, shopping, and cooking—and more time around the dinner table. You’ll serve up sticky, saucy baby back ribs and a creamy buttermilk ranch slaw, plus an epic take on mac ’n’ cheese with cavatappi noodles, Buffalo seasoning, pepper jack, white cheddar, and a spiced panko crust. If that’s not a perfect evening, we don’t know what is.
